# Exercise 006 - Create a secure route

1) Deploy a tomcat application. It will generate a service which respond to
   port 8080;

2) Expose the service;

3) Try connecting with protocol HTTP and HTTPS;

4) Delete the created route;

5) Generate a certificate;

6) Create an edge route passing the key and the certificate;

7) Try connecting with protocol HTTP and HTTPS;

8) Either if you obtain a publicly signed certificate, in a production
   environment there will be a problem. Can you identify it?

9) How can you solve this problem?
